Configuration entries:

KEY				TYPE	DESCRIPTION

Maximised			bool	True if the frame was last maximised

Network/
	IDEKey			string	The IDE key to match for incoming
					connections; if blank, all connections
					will be accepted
	Port			long	The TCP port to listen on

Perspective			string	The ConnectionPage perspective

Position/
	X			long	The last X position of the frame
	Y			long	The last Y position of the frame

Size/
	Height			long	The last height of the frame
	Width			long	The last width of the frame

SourcePanel/
	FontFace		string	Font to use for source display
	FontSize		long	Font size to use in points
	FontStyle		long	Font style
	FontWeight		long	Font weight
